{"hash":"gridsome","data":{"post":{"id":"158","title":"Gallery","summary":"\n<p>All images to share.</p>\n","body":"\n<p><em>Above image from wikimedia, Icons8, MIT license</em></p>\n<p>Thinking of a title and an abstract just to share a image is tired. So just merge all of the furture share in one post! The images are ordered from newer to older, making it both easy to read and easy to write.</p>\n<h3>\n      <a id=\"article-kaggle-course-certificate-2021-01-10\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#kaggle-course-certificate-2021-01-10\">\n      #</a> Kaggle Course Certificate <em>(2021-01-10)</em></h3>\n<p>First step to machine learning community!</p>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/104814646-1438f280-584b-11eb-8ba0-0a7929779684.png\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/104814646-1438f280-584b-11eb-8ba0-0a7929779684.png\" alt=\"Allan Chain - Intro to Machine Learning\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h3>\n      <a id=\"article-highest-so-week-rank-2020-09-12\" class=\"anchor-hover hash-link\" href=\"#highest-so-week-rank-2020-09-12\">\n      #</a> Highest SO Week Rank <em>(2020-09-12)</em></h3>\n<p>SO rewarded me 100 reputaion for reaching 200 reputation that week. <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"sweat_smile\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f605.png\">😅</g-emoji></p>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/104814707-6bd75e00-584b-11eb-99e3-1e8c9e99f032.jpg\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36528777/104814707-6bd75e00-584b-11eb-99e3-1e8c9e99f032.jpg\" alt=\"Snipaste_2020-09-12_17-41-20\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>","createdAt":"2021-01-16T14:46:40.000Z","lastEditedAt":"2021-01-16T14:46:40.000Z","image":"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7898809666b6cf6c7fb142be18bb7e3d85f5aa8d306d66ecc540a6fc38d85d3e/6874747